 "proto.h2": "Speaks every protocol that matters",
 "proto.openai": "Drop-in <span class=\"mono\">/v1/chat/completions</span>, models, embeddings, runs, and sessions — point existing clients at Jikji.",
 "proto.mcp": "Model Context Protocol server and client over stdio — consume MCP tools or expose Jikji as one.",
 "proto.acp": "Agent Communication Protocol over stdio for local process-based agent peers.",
