 "ops.h": "Operator tooling",
 "ops.p": "<span class=\"mono\">jikjictl</span> covers credentials and vault, RBAC, policy, audit queries, tracing, usage, and a marketplace — plus a separate web dashboard that never stores keys server-side.",
 "term.h": "Terminal-native",
 "term.p": "Interactive TUI chat, single-prompt mode, JSONL event streams for automation, and an MCP-shaped JSON-RPC mode — agents you can pipe.",
 "test.h": "Tested like infrastructure",
 "test.p": "A deterministic <span class=\"mono\">make verify</span> gate plus guarded live smoke tests against real providers. Benchmark, fuzz, property, and concurrency tests throughout the codebase.",
 "nav.start": "Get Started",
